{"tid":1804353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"過渡性房屋　林鄭：達標在望","createTime":"2019-12-31T02:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:28:43.000Z","uid":90397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d130f7d38339d3aa6655c7464ea8c412ecf977a","tid":1804353,"uid":90397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avP2Cog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavP2Cog.jpg&h=3e798a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社聯及樂善堂獲得會德豐地産借出逾50萬呎土地興建過渡性房屋。行政長官林鄭月娥在facebook專頁表示，相信經民、商、官通力合作，達標在望。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，今年《施政報告》提出在未來三年提供10000個過渡性房屋單位的目標，當時很多人都懷疑是否「吹水」；不到三個月，各界反應熱烈，包括私人發展商以象徵式租金提供土地，至今約8000個單位已到位。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥提到，不久前曾到九龍城參觀由樂善堂負責、全港第一個改建校舍作過渡性房屋的項目，知道今天再有由樂善堂負責的項目公布，相信憑藉它的經驗及熱誠，項目一定會取得成功。"},{"pid":"085a125f20f43de535de18d7e35a8a6ee3c6f707","tid":1804353,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=7e1f12ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=25e942ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要24000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=5099d680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要6000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=d3dc2ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}